IRC Bot... (yeah very inspired title) 

Requires:
* twisted
* txmongo (https://github.com/fiorix/mongo-async-python-driver/)
* lxml

A small irc bot that logs URLs posted in a IRC channel and store them in a mongodb. 
It will also:
    * download and store any images mentioned in a channel.
    * store quotes 
    * whatever...

How to run:
$ python ircbot.py <server> <channel> <nickname>
